PURPOSE:
--------
Minifly is designed to provide developers with a local development environment
that simulates the behavior of the Fly.io platform, allowing them to test and
debug applications before deploying to the actual Fly.io service.

For the official Fly.io platform, please visit: https://fly.io

For questions about this project, please visit: https://github.com/NoHeadDotDev/minifly